item.title: CVE-2023-40182|2024-09-30T18:18:19.411Z -- mesosoi -- silverwaregames-io-issue-tracker
item.description: Silverware Games is a premium social network where people can play games online. When using the Recovery form, a noticeably different amount of time passes depending of whether the specified email address presents in our database or not. This has been fixed in version 1.3.7.
